      "text": "Developer Workstation\n\nTerraform (Windows PowerShell)\n  Provisions EC2, Elastic IP,\n  Security Group, Key Pair\n\nAnsible (WSL2 / Linux)\n  Installs Docker, clones repo,\n  Deploys secrets + SSL cert,\n  Starts containers",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "dev-box",
      "originalText": "Developer Workstation\n\nTerraform (Windows PowerShell)\n  Provisions EC2, Elastic IP,\n  Security Group, Key Pair\n\nAnsible (WSL2 / Linux)\n  Installs Docker, clones repo,\n  Deploys secrets + SSL cert,\n  Starts containers",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
