      "text": "FreeRTC Server (Docker Container)\n\nNode.js + Express 5 (HTTPS :8001)\nSocket.IO Signaling + Chat Relay\nSession Auth (express-session)\nFriends API + Online Presence\n/api/rtc-config endpoint\nRoom Management (max 2 peers)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "freertc-box",
      "originalText": "FreeRTC Server (Docker Container)\n\nNode.js + Express 5 (HTTPS :8001)\nSocket.IO Signaling + Chat Relay\nSession Auth (express-session)\nFriends API + Online Presence\n/api/rtc-config endpoint\nRoom Management (max 2 peers)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
