      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "User A\nBrowser (Chrome/Firefox/Edge/Safari)\nor Electron Desktop App\n\nVoice PeerConnection (audio)\nVideo PeerConnection\n(camera / screen share)\n\nWeb Audio API Pipeline:\nmic > gain > analyser > dest\n\nRich Text Chat (Tiptap)\nEmoji + GIF + File Attachments\nRoom + Friends UI\nDevice Selection (mic, camera)\nAudio: NS, EC, AGC Settings",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "user-a-box",
      "originalText": "User A\nBrowser (Chrome/Firefox/Edge/Safari)\nor Electron Desktop App\n\nVoice PeerConnection (audio)\nVideo PeerConnection\n(camera / screen share)\n\nWeb Audio API Pipeline:\nmic > gain > analyser > dest\n\nRich Text Chat (Tiptap)\nEmoji + GIF + File Attachments\nRoom + Friends UI\nDevice Selection (mic, camera)\nAudio: NS, EC, AGC Settings",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
